{"type":null,"faqId":32969,"title":"通话过程中断，手机进入飞行模式如何处理？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>目前触发飞行模式主要通过两种方式：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>1、下拉信号栏中的快捷开关中触发。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2、长按电源键的菜单中触发。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>有可能部分用户手持电话的姿势特殊，导致距离传感器未贴近耳朵，通话时屏幕没有熄灭，误触发了信号栏中的飞行模式开关。建议用户调整信号栏“开关”中飞行模式的位置，</span><span class=\"s1\">例如移动到开关列表的最后，调整方法：信号栏“开关”页中点击最后一个图标，即可进入自定义快捷开关的界面。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":137,"faqType":"通话与联系人","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7671","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Calls-contacts","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748463000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":11,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"通话中断,飞行模式","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}